7ceef4b8524a319a23cB98dba6aa" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope=
" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !importa=
nt; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-s=
tyle: solid; background-color: #ccc;">  front-run crypto trades</a>, or bui=
ld infinitely leveraged crypto shadow banks, or steal money from customers;=
 all of that was interesting if you were interested in financial systems. I=
f you were interested in useful consumer products crypto was maybe less exc=
iting, but that=E2=80=99s not my beat so I couldn=E2=80=99t tell you.<a cla=
ss=3D"footnote-index" href=3D"#footnote-1" style=3D"color: #000000; text-de=
coration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #=
